comments.content: 20 week engagement closed - "Will head for Broadway"
"recently closed ten weeks at the Echo Tavern in Troy and was featured third on a bill in New York last week given for the benefit of tubercular patients."
"Female Impersonators"; "Also Other Big Acts"; "4—Shows Nightly—4"; Name corroborated since they appeared together at the Elm Lodge the day before.
"The Boy Who Has Completely Captivated Syracuse"
Johnny Kaye wants to book his six female impersonators into some Reno night club. They're marking time in Kansas City, awaiting reply.
"THE MALE SALLY RAND Dancing Her FAN and BUBBLE Dance"
"The Male Sally Rand Fan Dancer in New and Original Dance Creations"
"after eight weeks at Washington Club, East Liverpool, O., is heading east."
